<l>uṟuppottaṉ makkaḷop paṉṟāl veṟuttakka</l>
<l>paṇpotta loppatā moppu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Resemblance of bodies is no resemblance of souls true resemblance is the resemblance of qualities that attract.</l>
